fields.subject: SmartStart reminders: Pregnancy weeks 0 to 14
fields.content:
## Reminders for Pregnancy weeks 0-14

Things you'll need to think about in this phase of your pregnancy:
- choose a lead maternity carer

fields.subject: SmartStart reminders: Pregnancy weeks 15 to 30
fields.content:
## Reminders for Pregnancy weeks 15-30

Things you'll need to think about in this phase of your pregnancy:
- check what parental leave you can get 
- check what financial help you can get
- verify your identity with RealMe

fields.subject: SmartStart reminders: Pregnancy weeks 31 to birth
fields.content:
## Reminders for Pregnancy weeks 31 to birth

Things you'll need to think about in this phase of your pregnancy:
- get a car seat ready
- choose a Well Child Tamariki Ora provider

fields.subject: SmartStart reminders: New baby weeks 1 to 6
fields.content:
## Reminders for Your new baby weeks 1 to 6

Things you'll need to think about at this stage in your baby's life:
- register the birth
- apply for an IRD number for your child
- add your child to your Working for Families application
- If you're on a benefit, tell Ministry of Social Development your child has been born
- order a birth certificate

fields.subject: SmartStart reminders: Baby 6 weeks to 3 months
fields.content:
## Reminders for Your new baby 6 weeks to 3 months

Things you'll need to think about at this stage in your baby's life are:
- check if the financial help you can get has changed

fields.subject: SmartStart reminders: Baby 3 months to 6 months
fields.content:
## Reminders for Your new baby 3 months to 6 months

Things you'll need to think about at this stage in your baby's life:
- if you get Working for Families payments, let Inland Revenue know if your income changes 
- check if you can get help paying for childcare
